# Codex stores both authored configuration and runtime state in this directory.
# Track only the explicitly approved, portable configuration surfaces below.
*

!.gitignore
!README.md
!AGENTS.md
!config.toml
!*.config.toml
!hooks.json

!agents/
!agents/**

!bin/
!bin/**

!hooks/
!hooks/**

!rules/
!rules/**

!skills/
!skills/migrate-to-codex/
!skills/migrate-to-codex/**

**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.bak
*.sync-tmp
